        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="xm97tIzFpSOHS7XiSRMR-28" value="Of course this is only a theoretical abstraction. The same effect can be achieved without a true DAG implementation. By tracking the type of node connection and the depth in the DAG, we can achieve correct ordering of the steps in the pipeline. The ordering of steps at the same depth is irrelevant. Thus the main challenge is to track which elements have been added" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
